                 <h3> <a class="anchor" id="top" name="fun"></a>Family Fun at All Saints, Sanderstead. Sunday 14th October, 3pm
                 </h3>
                 <p>Family Fun is a monthly activity based service  for all children up to the age of 12 years, and their parents​, grandparents​ and carers. We start at 3:00pm in the All Saints' church halls in Onslow Gardens, with ​lots of ​time for activities and crafts based around ​the Bible, ​which the children do with their parents and carers, ​followed by plenty of ​lively ​singing​ and a story. We end our time together​ with a tasty snack and refreshments for all. Children take home everything they have made.</p>
                 <p>We look forward to welcoming you​ to Family Fun.  If you have any questions, please email ​children@sanderstead-parish.org.uk </p>
                 </p>
